      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "53bb1ec393e54ed0",
      "text": "Two paths can be imagined here, which could also be taken in a complementary way: the rejection of demands and the overcoming of ecological growth limits of subsystemic service production. Both ways, however, offer, to say the least, no guarantee for a lasting compatibility of demands and what is ecologically possible."
